      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know u aren't a doctor but i've read so much about manuka honey and how it's used in hospitals for wound healing... it's like a natural antibiotic right? it seems way safer and less intense than going to an ER for stitches if it can just seal the wound and keep bacteria out. don't u think it could actually work for a cut like this?",
